---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="页面未找到">
  <div
    class="max-w-content py-32 md:py-40 text-center flex flex-col items-center"
  >
    <p
      class="text-7xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-border)] mb-6 tracking-tight"
    >
      404
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">页面未找到</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] max-w-md mb-8 leading-relaxed">
      你访问的页面不存在或者已经被移除。请检查链接是否正确，或者返回首页浏览其他内容。
    </p>
    <a
      href="/"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-text)] text-[var(--color-bg)] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium no-underline hover:opacity-85 transition-opacity"
    >
      返回首页
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>